  <description><![CDATA[<p>Formigal makes a welcome return to our programme this winter. It boasts a 137km ski area which extends over four valleys all linked by an efficient lift system and free shuttle bus service connecting each base. Queues for the lifts are rare outside peak holiday times and it is a great place for mixed ability parties with a choice of red or blue runs from most chairlifts. Formigal village itself has a great atmosphere and has an excellent range of activities and some lively après-ski. Our new flight to Huesca will significantly reduce transfer times.</p>]]></description>
