  <generalInformation><![CDATA[<p><strong>Beginners skiing in Formigal </strong></p>
<p>There are fast chairlifts linking each of the four valleys and the nursery slopes for beginners are excellent. Unusually, there are runs for all standards on the higher slopes. There are also special family zones and slow ski zones</p>
<p><strong>Intermediates skiing in <strong>Formigal</strong><br /></strong></p>
<p>intermediates in particular will find a very wide choice across all four valleys.</p>
<p><strong>Advanced skiing in <strong>Formigal</strong><br /></strong></p>
<p>Advanced skiers are spoilt with no less than three free ride areas. Experienced skiers can even take a snowcat above Portalet and explore the remote runs down to Anayet and the best powder in the resort</p>
<p><strong>Snowboarders in <strong>Formigal</strong><br /></strong></p>
<p>Snowboarders are spoilt with an excellent snowpark and a boardercross.</p>]]></generalInformation>
